Dialogue: 100,0:08:13.88,0:08:14.80,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}哦，这个，你当然可以相信\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, well,of course you can.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.82,0:08:16.12,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你估计已经预见到一切了\N{\fnArial\fs32}You probably foresaw the whole thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}当然！一点都不惊讶\N{\fnArial\fs32}Of course!No surprises here.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.46,0:08:23.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我从未想过能亲眼见到黄钻\N{\fnArial\fs32}I never expected to seeYellow Diamond in person.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}多么威严啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}What a commanding presence.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你能在她身上直接感受到\N{\fnArial\fs32}You can just feelstrength and confidence
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.13,0:08:29.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}那份力量和自信\N{\fnArial\fs32}radiating from her.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.62,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}不要误会我，当然了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Don't misunderstand me,of course.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.00,0:08:34.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我永远都会衷心于蓝钻\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'll always bein Blue's confidence,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.40,0:08:36.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}但如果我生来为黄钻效力\N{\fnArial\fs32}but if I had been made for Yellow,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.62,0:08:38.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我也不会有怨言的\N{\fnArial\fs32}you wouldn't see me complaining.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.60,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我希望她们会欣赏我\N{\fnArial\fs32}I do hope they appreciate all my hard work
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.35,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}辛苦保留下的粉钻的遗产\N{\fnArial\fs32}to preserve the Pink Diamond legacy.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}这样我被分配到这里\N{\fnArial\fs32}It would really make it worth being stationed here
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.13,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}指挥这些可怜的宝石们也值了\N{\fnArial\fs32}with these sorry excuses for Gems.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.48,0:08:51.24,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}哦！当然，太可惜了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ohhh!It's a shame, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:51.64,0:08:53.46,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}这个哨位太偏远了\N{\fnArial\fs32}This out post is so remote.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.73,0:08:56.22,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我甚至开始觉得我们被遗忘了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I was beginning to think we'd been forgotten.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.30,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}但我们还没有！\N{\fnArial\fs32}But we haven't!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}见到两颗钻石——在一天内！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Two Diamonds -- one day!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.57,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}多大的荣誉啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}What an honor.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.91,0:09:05.00,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}没什么能搅乱我心情了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I don't think anythingcould spoil this for me.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.86,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}这…是……\N{\fnArial\fs32}What...is...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.85,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}什么意思？！\N{\fnArial\fs32}the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}这两只怎么逃离控制区域了？！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Why are these twooutside the containment area?!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.89,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}霍利蓝玛瑙，我可以解释\N{\fnArial\fs32}Holly Blue, I can explain.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.13,0:09:23.33,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}不需要了，您的明晰\N{\fnArial\fs32}No need, your Clarity.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.19,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}可能您都无法预料到\N{\fnArial\fs32}Not even you could have foreseen
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}这些紫晶有多不可靠！\N{\fnArial\fs32}how incompetent these Amethysts are.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}当然，如果想让一切走上正路\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, if you want something done right,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:30.47,0:09:32.93,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你只能亲自动手\N{\fnArial\fs32}you just do it yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.91,0:09:37.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你们两个跟我走！\N{\fnArial\fs32}You two are coming with me!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Garnet!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.73,0:09:45.51,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}史蒂文，带格雷格上船！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven,get Greg on board!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.55,0:09:46.71,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}好的，拜托了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, please!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.45,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}交给我们吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}We'll handle this noise.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.55,0:09:55.72,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}哦哦哦！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ooooooh!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:55.76,0:09:57.66,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}这一天我等了好久了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I've been waiting to do this all day.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}呃！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Unh!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.73,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你们在干什么呢？！她们是叛徒！\N{\fnArial\fs32}What are you doing?!They're traitors!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}毁掉她们！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Destroy them!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.70,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}再见！再见！再见！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Bye!Bye!        Bye!- Bye!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.64,0:10:11.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}一生荣誉，紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs32}Famethyst for life!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.21,0:10:12.91,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我会向钻石通报你们的！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'll report youto the Diamonds!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.93,0:10:15.55,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你们全部！全部都会被粉碎！\N{\fnArial\fs32}All of you!You'll all be shattered!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.68,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你真的打算告诉钻石们\N{\fnArial\fs32}You're really gonna tell the Diamonds
Dialogue: 100,0:10:17.68,0:10:20.18,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你允许了一群叛徒\N{\fnArial\fs32}that you allowed a band of traitorous rebels
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.75,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}大摇大摆进入了一个戒备森严的机构\N{\fnArial\fs32}to infiltrate a highly secure facility
Dialogue: 100,0:10:22.78,0:10:26.06,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}然后在你眼皮底下溜走了？\N{\fnArial\fs32}and escape from right under your careful watch?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.53,0:10:30.53,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}听上去不像什么明智之举哦，霍利\N{\fnArial\fs32}Doesn't sound like a wise thing to do, Holly Blue.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.88,0:10:35.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}所以为了你自己，管好你的嘴巴\N{\fnArial\fs32}So do yourself a favorand keep your mouth shut.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.91,0:10:37.44,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}就这样吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}That will be all.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:46.74,0:10:48.42,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}太谢谢你们来救我了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Thanks so muchfor coming to get me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.64,0:10:52.31,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}这算是我人生中第三疯狂的周末了\N{\fnArial\fs32}That has to be likethe third-craziest weekend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.95,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}爸爸，对不起，我让你卷入了这一切\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad, I'm really sorryI got you into all this.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:56.60,0:11:00.08,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}这一切都只是因为我的好奇心\N{\fnArial\fs32}This whole thing started cause I wanted answers.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.46,0:11:02.37,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}你不需要为任何事感到抱歉\N{\fnArial\fs32}You don't have to be sorry about a thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.17,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我希望你找到了你想要的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I hope you found what you were looking for.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.66,0:11:06.15,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我找到了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I did.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:06.88,0:11:07.77,Normal Dialog Text,General,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42.667}我找到了你\N{\fnArial\fs32}I found you.
